convert ima.jpg -resize 1024X768 output.jpg     - change resolution
convert img.jpg -quality 80 output.jpg          - reduce size 
convert img.jpg out.pdf                         - convert image to a pdf
montage -geometry +2+2 img.jpg img.jpg out.jpg  - create a collage

-- Effects
convert -modulate 200 img.jpg out.jpg      - increase decrease brightness
convert -modulate 200,250 img.jpg out.jpg  - saturation: 1st value is for brightness and 2nd is for saturation
convert -charcoal 1 img.jpg out.jpg        - charcoal effect
convert -paint 6 img.jpg out.jpg           - paint effect
convert -blur 0X10 img.jpg out.jpg         - blur image
convert -negate img.jpg out.jpg            - negative effect
convert -colorspace GRAY img.jpg out.jpg   - B&W
convert -bordercolor green -border 20 img.jpg out.jpg        - create border
convert -background black -vignette 200X200 img.jpg out.jpg  - lesser the number is more stronger effact
